title: BRIEF-Iac/InterActiveCorp Says CEO Joseph Levin's 2017 Total Compensation Was $13 Million
text:
April 30, 2018 / 8:40 PM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-Iac/InterActiveCorp Says CEO Joseph Levin's 2017 Total Compensation Was $13 Million Reuters Staff 1 Min Read
 IAC/InterActiveCorp:
* IAC/INTERACTIVECORP SAYS CEO JOSEPH LEVIN’S 2017 TOTAL COMPENSATION WAS $13 MILLION VERSUS $10.5 MILLION IN 2016 – SEC FILING
* IAC/INTERACTIVECORP SAYS CFO GLENN H. SCHIFFMAN'S 2017 TOTAL COMPENSATION WAS $7 MILLION – SEC FILING Source : bit.ly/2FucMj5 Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
